text: Jeong Hae-rim (born 16 December 1995) is a South Korean snowboarder. She competed in the 2013, 2015 and 2017 FIS Snowboard World Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in parallel giant slalom. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of South Korea Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Snowboarders at the 2017 Asian Winter Games Category:Universiade gold medalists for South Korea Category:Universiade bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Universiade medalists in snowboarding Category:Competitors at the 2019 Winter Universiade
